  "detailed_description": "<h1>Just Updated</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This Game is STILL Under Development</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I did a whole rework of the game to focus more on the Gameplay.<br>The new Gameplay is now very close to my vision, and stays true to what I love about combat oriented Games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Thank you for adding this Game to your wishlist :D</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Mag</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>REFLEX BASED DECISION MAKING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181220/extras/3b2d843d0754bcca18073e7adbe2a7de.poster.avif?t=1741735191\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181220/extras/3b2d843d0754bcca18073e7adbe2a7de.webm?t=1741735191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181220/extras/3b2d843d0754bcca18073e7adbe2a7de.mp4?t=1741735191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blend <strong>gunplay</strong>, and <strong>hand-to-hand combat</strong>, to eliminate waves of enemies with brutal efficiency. Master the art of the fight. Every little decision matters. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181220/extras/94c91c6a0ce51bd7a28a45f09e5047f7.poster.avif?t=1741735191\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181220/extras/94c91c6a0ce51bd7a28a45f09e5047f7.webm?t=1741735191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181220/extras/94c91c6a0ce51bd7a28a45f09e5047f7.mp4?t=1741735191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>INTENSE BOSS DUELS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181220/extras/10156f8207b8b7c4589feb7321bed3ca.poster.avif?t=1741735191\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181220/extras/10156f8207b8b7c4589feb7321bed3ca.webm?t=1741735191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181220/extras/10156f8207b8b7c4589feb7321bed3ca.mp4?t=1741735191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everything you've learned will be tested by a variety of competent  bosses. Each enemy presents a <strong>unique challenge</strong>. They're not bullet sponges; you’ll need to analyze their patterns and weaknesses, coming up with creative, precise strategies to defeat them. Your arsenal is only part of the equation—<strong>your mind is your deadliest weapon.</strong><br><br>Until you face the Ultimate challenger,<br><strong>YOUR OWN SHADOW</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181220/extras/ca0cabe971a39e040f321da382c546f6.avif?t=1741735191\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181220/extras_big/ca0cabe971a39e040f321da382c546f6.avif?t=1741735191 width=800 height=450 /></span><strong></strong></p>",
